@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .login-page {
            display: flex;
            /*height: 100vh;*/
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .login-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100%;
            max-height: 1500px;
            width: 1500px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .login-image {
            flex: 1;
            background: url('~/Assets/Login/login1.png') center center/cover no-repeat;
        }
/**/
        .About-form {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

            .About-form h2 {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                font-size: 28px;
                color: #333;
            }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #f88379;
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            .btn:hover {
                background-color: #e87063;
            }

        .form-group p {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .form-group p a {
                color: #f88379;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

                .form-group p a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }
    </style>
    <title> EduTech - Login</title>
</head>

<div class="login-page">
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-image">
            <img src="~/Assets/Logo/Minimalist E Logo.png" alt="halo" />
        </div>
        <div class="About-form">
            <h1 class="text-left" style="color:red; font-family:sans-serif"><strong>EduTech</strong></h1>

            <p>Welcome to Edutech, where innovation meets education. We are a cutting-edge Learning Management System (LMS) designed to transform the way you teach and learn. At Edutech, we believe in the power of technology to enhance educational experiences, making learning more interactive, engaging, and effective.</p>
            <h4><strong>Our Mission</strong></h4>
            <p>Our mission is to provide educators and students with a dynamic and interactive platform that fosters a love for learning. We aim to bridge the gap between traditional education and modern technology, creating an environment where knowledge can thrive and grow.</p>
            <br />
            <h4><strong>Our Vision</strong></h4>
            <p>We envision a world where education is not confined by boundaries. A world where every learner has access to quality education, driven by innovation and technology. At Edutech, we are committed to making this vision a reality.
              Join us on this exciting journey towards a brighter, more informed future. Let's embrace the future of education together with Edutech.</p>
            <br />
            <h4><strong>What We Offer</strong></h4>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Interactive Learning Tools</strong> : Our platform is equipped with a variety of interactive tools that make learning fun and engaging. From quizzes and multimedia presentations to virtual classrooms and forums, Edutech brings education to life.</li>
                <li><strong>Personalized Learning Paths</strong> : We understand that each student is unique. Our system allows for personalized learning experiences tailored to individual needs and pace, ensuring that every learner can achieve their full potential.</li>
                <li><strong>Collaborative Environment</strong> : Edutech fosters collaboration between students and teachers. Our platform supports group projects, peer reviews, and open discussions, encouraging a community-based approach to learning.</li>
                <li><strong>Easy Accessibility</strong> : With Edutech, learning is accessible anytime, anywhere. Our mobile-friendly design ensures that students and educators can stay connected and continue their educational journey seamlessly across different devices.</li>
            </ul>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    @Scripts.Render("~/bundles/jqueryval")
}

